#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid "<span class=\"h1-fs\"><strong>Basics:</strong></span>"
msgstr "<span class=\"h1-fs\"><strong>ພື້ນຖານ:</strong></span>"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid "<span class=\"h1-fs\"><strong>Do you want to go further?</strong></span>"
msgstr "<span class=\"h1-fs\"><strong>ທ່ານຕ້ອງການໄປຕໍ່ບໍ່?</strong></span>"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid "<span class=\"h1-fs\"><strong>Use case:</strong></span>"
msgstr "<span class=\"h1-fs\"><strong>ກໍລະນີການນຳໃຊ້:</strong></span>"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>1. Flow 1:</strong> Most products need a human assessment as the "
"remaining quantity cannot be automatically computed. For those, a Recurring "
"Task is created in the Project App. This task reappears every week, and you "
"can personalize it with a checklist to avoid forgetting anything."
msgstr ""
"<strong>1. ຂັ້ນຕອນທີ 1:</strong> ສິນຄ້າສ່ວນໃຫຍ່ຕ້ອງການການປະເມີນໂດຍຄົນ ເນື່ອງຈາກຈຳນວນທີ່ເຫຼືອບໍ່"
"ສາມາດຄິດໄລ່ແບບອັດຕະໂນມັດໄດ້. ສຳລັບສິນຄ້າເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນ, ວຽກທີ່ເກີດຂຶ້ນຊ້ຳ (Recurring Task) ຈະຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນ"
"ໃນແອັບໂຄງການ (Project). ວຽກນີ້ຈະກັບມາປະກົດຂຶ້ນທຸກໆອາທິດ, ແລະ ທ່ານສາມາດປັບແຕ່ງມັນດ້ວຍລາຍການກ"
"ວດສອບ (checklist) ເພື່ອບໍ່ໃຫ້ຫຼົງລືມສິ່ງໃດສິ່ງໜຶ່ງ."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>2. Flow 2:</strong> For products that can be tracked, such as "
"bottled beers and sodas, you can use automated purchases. To try it, "
"navigate to your Point of Sale and sell a Blond Beer to a customer."
msgstr ""
"<strong>2. ຂັ້ນຕອນທີ 2:</strong> ສຳລັບສິນຄ້າທີ່ສາມາດຕິດຕາມໄດ້ ເຊັ່ນ: ເບຍຂວດ ແລະ ນ້ຳອັດລົມ, ທ່"
"ານສາມາດໃຊ້ການຊື້ແບບອັດຕະໂນມັດ. ເພື່ອທົດລອງໃຊ້, ໃຫ້ໄປທີ່ຈຸດຂາຍ (Point of Sale) ແລະ ຂາຍເບຍ "
"Blond Beer ໃຫ້ກັບລູກຄ້າ."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong><span class=\"display-4-fs\">Bar</span></strong><br/>"
msgstr "<strong><span class=\"display-4-fs\">ບາ</span></strong><br/>"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"A free, personalized, integrated <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Website</font></strong> in a few clicks. Start receiving orders directly in Odoo or go live with your \n"
"                        <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">E-shop</font></strong> in a few minutes."
msgstr ""
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ເວັບໄຊ</font></strong> ທີ່ປະສົມປະສານ ແລະ ປັ"
"ບແຕ່ງໄດ້ເອງແບບຟຣີໆ ພຽງແຕ່ບໍ່ກີ່ຄລິກ. ເລີ່ມຮັບການສັ່ງຊື້ໂດຍກົງໃນ Odoo ຫຼື ເປີດໃຊ້ <strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">ຮ້ານຄ້າອອນລາຍ (E-shop)</font></strong> ຂອງທ່ານໃນບໍ່ກີ່ນາທີ."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"At the end of your service, remember to close your register. To do so, in "
"the Point of Sale App, select \"Close Register\" in the top-right menu. You "
"can then precise your cash amount and validate the closing."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອສິ້ນສຸດການບໍລິການຂອງທ່ານ, ຢ່າລືມປິດຮອບການຂາຍ. ເພື່ອດຳເນີນການ, ໃນແອັບຈຸດຂາຍ (Point of "
"Sale), ໃຫ້ເລືອກ \"ປິດຮອບການຂາຍ (Close Register)\" ໃນເມນູຂວາເທິງ. ຈາກນັ້ນທ່ານສາມາດລະບຸຈ"
"ຳນວນເງິນສົດ ແລະ ຢືນຢັນການປິດໄດ້."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model:planning.role,name:bar_industry.planning_role_2
msgid "Bar"
msgstr "ບາ"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model:planning.role,name:bar_industry.planning_role_3
msgid "Bar & Service"
msgstr "ບາ ແລະ ການບໍລິການ"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid "Basics:"
msgstr "ພື້ນຖານ:"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model:product.template,name:bar_industry.product_product_26_product_template
msgid "Blond Beer"
msgstr "ເບຍ Blond Beer"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid "By doing so, you have only 23 beers left in your stock."
msgstr "ດ້ວຍການເຮັດແບບນັ້ນ, ທ່ານຈະເຫຼືອເບຍພຽງແຕ່ 23 ຂວດໃນຄັງສິນຄ້າຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"By the way, you can see another project with recurring tasks. This one is a "
"demo for cleaning tasks."
msgstr ""
"ນອກຈາກນັ້ນ, ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດເຫັນໂຄງການອື່ນທີ່ມີວຽກທີ່ເກີດຂຶ້ນຊ້ຳ. ອັນນີ້ແມ່ນການສາທິດສຳລັບວຽກການອະນາໄມ."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"By uploading this module's demo data, your database has been filled with a "
"few products."
msgstr ""
"ໂດຍການອັບໂຫຼດຂໍ້ມູນສາທິດຂອງໂມດູນນີ້, ຖານຂໍ້ມູນຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ຖືກຕື່ມດ້ວຍສິນຄ້າຈຳນວນໜຶ່ງ."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model:project.project,name:bar_industry.project_project_2
msgid "Cleaning"
msgstr "ການອະນາໄມ"

