#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Discover the basics of this package and explore all the possibilities Odoo "
"offers to improve your experience."
msgstr ""
"ຄົ້ນຫາພື້ນຖານຂອງຊຸດເຄື່ອງມືນີ້ ແລະ ສຳຫຼວດຄວາມເປັນໄປໄດ້ທັງໝົດທີ່ Odoo ມອບໃຫ້ເພື່ອປັບປຸງປະສົບການຂອງທ່າ"
"ນ."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid "Do you want to go further?"
msgstr "ທ່ານຕ້ອງການໄປຕໍ່ບໍ່?"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Don't forget to hit the \"Order\" button each time you change an order. This"
" will forward the order to the Kitchen Display."
msgstr ""
"ຢ່າລືມກົດປຸ່ມ \"ສັ່ງຊື້ (Order)\" ທຸກຄັ້ງທີ່ທ່ານປ່ຽນແປງລາຍການສັ່ງ. ອັນນີ້ຈະສົ່ງລາຍການສັ່ງໄປຍັງໜ້າຈໍສະແດງຜົ"
"ນໃນເຮືອນຄົວ."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model:project.task.type,name:bar_industry.project_task_type_2
msgid "Done"
msgstr "ຈົບເເລັວ"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid "From the Point of Sale, open your register on the main dashboard."
msgstr "ຈາກຈຸດຂາຍ (Point of Sale), ໃຫ້ເປີດຮອບການຂາຍຂອງທ່ານໃນໜ້າຈໍຫຼັກ."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Go to your Purchase App to easily create Requests for Proposal or Purchase "
"Orders."
msgstr ""
"ໄປທີ່ແອັບການຈັດຊື້ (Purchase) ເພື່ອສ້າງໃບສະເໜີລາຄາ ຫຼື ໃບສັ່ງຊື້ໄດ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍດາຍ."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model:product.pricelist,name:bar_industry.product_pricelist_2
msgid "Happy Hour"
msgstr "Happy Hour"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid "Hello there!"
msgstr "ສະບາຍດີ!"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you navigate to your Purchase App, you can see a new Purchase Order that "
"is ready to be sent. You can choose a packaging if your product has an "
"existing one."
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າທ່ານໄປທີ່ແອັບການຈັດຊື້, ທ່ານຈະເຫັນໃບສັ່ງຊື້ໃໝ່ທີ່ພ້ອມຈະສົ່ງ. ທ່ານສາມາດເລືອກບັນຈຸພັນໄດ້ຫາກສິນຄ້າຂອງທ່ານມີ"
"ຢູ່ແລ້ວ."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you want to assign them an Odoo user account, you can select a related "
"user in the \"HR Settings\" tab."
msgstr ""
"ຫາກທ່ານຕ້ອງການກຳນົດບັນຊີຜູ້ໃຊ້ Odoo ໃຫ້ພວກເຂົາ, ທ່ານສາມາດເລືອກຜູ້ໃຊ້ທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງໃນແຖບ \"ການຕັ້ງຄ່າ "
"HR\"."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you want to execute a practical guided tour of this module, you should "
"Import demo data and try the Demo - Use Case (In the next Knowledge "
"Article)."
msgstr ""
"ຫາກທ່ານຕ້ອງການທົດລອງໃຊ້ໂມດູນນີ້ຕາມຂັ້ນຕອນ, ທ່ານຄວນນຳເຂົ້າຂໍ້ມູນສາທິດ ແລະ ລອງໃຊ້ Demo - Use "
"Case (ໃນບົດຄວາມຄວາມຮູ້ຖັດໄປ)."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage all your communication channels in one place with Odoo <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Marketing Automation</font></strong>, <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Email Marketing</font></strong>, \n"
"                        <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Social Media Marketing</font></strong>, and <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">SMS Marketing</font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"ຈັດການທຸກຊ່ອງທາງການສື່ສານຂອງທ່ານໃນບ່ອນດຽວກັບ Odoo <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-"
"1\">ການຕະຫຼາດອັດຕະໂນມັດ</font></strong>, <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">"
"ການຕະຫຼາດຜ່ານອີເມວ</font></strong>, \n"
"                        <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ການຕະຫຼາດຜ່ານສື່ສັງ"
"ຄົມອອນລາຍ</font></strong>, ແລະ <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ການຕະຫຼາດ"
"ຜ່ານ SMS</font></strong>."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage your accounting easier than ever with a completely integrated "
"environment. (<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Accounting "
"App</font></strong>)"
msgstr ""
"ຈັດການບັນຊີຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ງ່າຍກວ່າທີ່ເຄີຍດ້ວຍລະບົບທີ່ປະສານງານກັນຢ່າງສົມບູນ. (<strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">ແອັບບັນຊີ</font></strong>)"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo is entirely integrated into an App. Download it to turn your phone into"
" an additional cashier (and much more)."
msgstr ""
"Odoo ໄດ້ຖືກລວມເຂົ້າໃນແອັບດຽວຢ່າງສົມບູນ. ດາວໂຫຼດມັນເພື່ອປ່ຽນໂທລະສັບຂອງທ່ານໃຫ້ເປັນເຄື່ອງຄິດເງິນເພີ່ມເຕີ"
"ມ (ແລະ ອື່ນໆອີກຫຼາຍຢ່າງ)."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid "Odoo offers you infinite possibilities, such as:"
msgstr "Odoo ມອບຄວາມເປັນໄປໄດ້ທີ່ບໍ່ມີຂີດຈຳກັດໃຫ້ທ່ານ ເຊັ່ນ:"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Of course, this is just an overview of the features included in this "
"package. Feel free to add new apps, delete/modify demo data, and test "
"everything around!"
msgstr ""
"ແນ່ນອນ, ນີ້ແມ່ນພຽງແຕ່ພາບລວມຂອງຄຸນສົມບັດທີ່ມີຢູ່ໃນຊຸດເຄື່ອງມືນີ້. ທ່ານສາມາດເພີ່ມແອັບໃໝ່, ລຶບ ຫຼື ແກ້ໄຂຂໍ້ມູນສ"
"າທິດ ແລະ ທົດລອງໃຊ້ທຸກຢ່າງໄດ້ຕາມໃຈ!"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once the products are there, you can click the \"Receipt\" smart button to "
"validate your receipt and add these new products to your stock."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອສິນຄ້າມາຮອດແລ້ວ, ທ່ານສາມາດຄລິກປຸ່ມ \"ໃບຮັບສິນຄ້າ (Receipt)\" ເພື່ອຢືນຢັນການຮັບ ແລະ ເພີ່ມສິນຄ້"
"າໃໝ່ເຫຼົ່ານີ້ເຂົ້າໃນຄັງສິນຄ້າຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Organise your events and connect with your customers easily with the<strong>"
" <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Events App</font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"ຈັດງານກິດຈະກຳຂອງທ່ານ ແລະ ເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ກັບລູກຄ້າໄດ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍດາຍດ້ວຍ <strong> <font class=\"text-"
"o-color-1\">ແອັບກິດຈະກຳ (Events)</font></strong>."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid "Plan your services easily using the Planning App."
msgstr "ວາງແຜນການບໍລິການຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍດາຍໂດຍໃຊ້ແອັບການວາງແຜນ (Planning)."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid "Reach us"
msgstr "ຕິດຕໍ່ພວກເຮົາ"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Reordering rules are displayed in the smart buttons on top of your product. "
"You can see a minimum quantity, and a maximum. Each time the forecast stock "
"lowers beneath the minimum stock, it automatically creates a purchase order "
"to replenish to the maximum quantity."
msgstr ""
"ກົດເກນການສັ່ງຊື້ຄືນໃໝ່ຈະຖືກສະແດງຢູ່ໃນປຸ່ມລັດຢູ່ດ້ານເທິງຂອງສິນຄ້າຂອງທ່ານ. ທ່ານສາມາດເຫັນຈຳນວນຕ່ຳສຸດ ແລ"
"ະ ສູງສຸດ. ທຸກຄັ້ງທີ່ສິນຄ້າຄົງຄັງທີ່ຄາດການໄວ້ຫຼຸດລົງຕ່ຳກວ່າເກນຕ່ຳສຸດ, ລະບົບຈະສ້າງໃບສັ່ງຊື້ໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດເພື່ອຕື່"
"ມສິນຄ້າໃຫ້ຮອດຈຳນວນສູງສຸດ."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Replenishment is essential but challenging for a bar owner to systematize."
msgstr ""
"ການຕື່ມສິນຄ້າເປັນສິ່ງທີ່ຈຳເປັນ ແຕ່ເປັນສິ່ງທີ່ທ້າທາຍສຳລັບເຈົ້າຂອງບາໃນການຈັດລະບົບ."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model:planning.role,name:bar_industry.planning_role_1
msgid "Service"
msgstr "ບໍລິການ"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model:project.project,name:bar_industry.project_project_1
msgid "Suppliers Orders"
msgstr "ລາຍການສັ່ງຊື້ຈາກຜູ້ສະໜອງ"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model:project.project,label_tasks:bar_industry.project_project_1
#: model:project.project,label_tasks:bar_industry.project_project_2
msgid "Tasks"
msgstr "ວຽກ"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Kitchen Display</font></strong> "
"will ensure a great follow up of every order in your bar and kitchen."
msgstr ""
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ໜ້າຈໍສະແດງຜົນໃນເຮືອນຄົວ</font></strong> ຈະຊ່"
"ວຍໃຫ້ການຕິດຕາມທຸກການສັ່ງຊື້ໃນບາ ແລະ ເຮືອນຄົວຂອງທ່ານເປັນໄປຢ່າງດີຢ້ຽມ."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The stock is only updated when you close your register. Let's do it before "
"continuing to the next step."
msgstr ""
"ສິນຄ້າຄົງຄັງຈະຖືກອັບເດດເມື່ອທ່ານປິດຮອບການຂາຍເທົ່ານັ້ນ. ໃຫ້ດຳເນີນການກ່ອນຈະໄປຂັ້ນຕອນຕໍ່ໄປ."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"These all go free in your current subscription; feel free to explore! 🙃"
msgstr "ທັງໝົດນີ້ແມ່ນຟຣີໃນການສະໝັກໃຊ້ປະຈຸບັນຂອງທ່ານ; ສາມາດສຳຫຼວດໄດ້ຕາມໃຈ! 🙃"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model:project.task.type,name:bar_industry.project_task_type_1
msgid "To Do"
msgstr "ສິ່ງທີ່ຈະເຮັດ"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid "Use case:"
msgstr "ກໍລະນີການນຳໃຊ້:"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Inventory App</font></strong>"
" to manage your stock and receive products."
msgstr ""
"ໃຊ້ <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ແອັບຄັງສິນຄ້າ (Inventory)</font></"
"strong> ເພື່ອຈັດການສິນຄ້າ ແລະ ຮັບສິນຄ້າ."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Planning App</font></strong> "
"to schedule your shifts and share it with your employees."
msgstr ""
"ໃຊ້ <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ແອັບການວາງແຜນ (Planning)</font></"
"strong> ເພື່ອກຳນົດກະການເຮັດວຽກ ແລະ ແບ່ງປັນໃຫ້ກັບພະນັກງານຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Point of Sale</font></strong>"
" for your sales at the desk. You can also download the Odoo Mobile App on "
"any phone to take orders."
msgstr ""
"ໃຊ້ <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ຈຸດຂາຍ (Point of Sale)</font></"
"strong> ສຳລັບການຂາຍຢູ່ທີ່ເຄົາເຕີ. ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດດາວໂຫຼດແອັບ Odoo Mobile ໃນໂທລະສັບເພື່ອຮັບການສັ່ງ"
"ຊື້ໄດ້."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Project App</font></strong> "
"to never miss a reordering or a cleaning task."
msgstr ""
"ໃຊ້ <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ແອັບໂຄງການ (Project)</font></"
"strong> ເພື່ອບໍ່ໃຫ້ພາດການສັ່ງຊື້ຄືນໃໝ່ ຫຼື ວຽກການອະນາໄມ."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Purchase App</font></strong> "
"to reorder your products."
msgstr ""
"ໃຊ້ <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ແອັບການຈັດຊື້ (Purchase)</font></"
"strong> ເພື່ອສັ່ງຊື້ສິນຄ້າຂອງທ່ານຄືນໃໝ່."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:web_tour.tour,rainbow_man_message:bar_industry.knowledge_tour
msgid "Welcome! Happy exploring."
msgstr "ຍິນດີຕ້ອນຮັບ! ຂໍໃຫ້ມ່ວນກັບການສຳຫຼວດ."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid "Would you like to discuss your Odoo setup with us or go even further?"
msgstr "ທ່ານຕ້ອງການປຶກສາກ່ຽວກັບການຕັ້ງຄ່າ Odoo ກັບພວກເຮົາ ຫຼື ຕ້ອງການໄປຕໍ່ບໍ່?"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can access every installed App in your Odoo database on your main "
"dashboard."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດເຂົ້າເຖິງທຸກແອັບທີ່ຕິດຕັ້ງແລ້ວໃນຖານຂໍ້ມູນ Odoo ຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ໃນໜ້າຈໍຫຼັກ."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can easily edit the floor map by clicking \"Edit plan\" in the top-right"
" menu when on the table selection of your Point of Sale."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດແກ້ໄຂແຜນຜັງໄດ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍດາຍໂດຍການຄລິກ \"ແກ້ໄຂແຜນຜັງ (Edit plan)\" ໃນເມນູຂວາເທິງ ເ"
"ມື່ອຢູ່ໃນໜ້າເລືອກໂຕະຂອງຈຸດຂາຍ."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can now email your Request for Proposal to your vendor or confirm it "
"manually."
msgstr ""
"ຕອນນີ້ທ່ານສາມາດສົ່ງອີເມວໃບສະເໜີລາຄາໄປໃຫ້ຜູ້ຂາຍຂອງທ່ານ ຫຼື ຢືນຢັນດ້ວຍຕົນເອງ."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can see that there is a reordering rule configured for this product if "
"you go to Inventory  &amp;gt; Products  &amp;gt; Blond Beer"
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດເຫັນໄດ້ວ່າມີການຕັ້ງຄ່າກົດເກນການສັ່ງຊື້ຄືນໃໝ່ສຳລັບສິນຄ້ານີ້ ຫາກທ່ານໄປທີ່ ຄັງສິນຄ້າ (Inventory) "
"&amp;gt; ສິນຄ້າ (Products) &amp;gt; Blond Beer"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You completed that demo use case! There are millions of other ways to adapt "
"your Odoo setup to fit your business needs."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານໄດ້ສຳເລັດການທົດລອງໃຊ້ນີ້ແລ້ວ! ຍັງມີອີກຫຼາຍລ້ານວິທີໃນການປັບແຕ່ງ Odoo ໃຫ້ເໝາະສົມກັບຄວາມຕ້ອງການທາ"
"ງທຸລະກິດຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You currently have two steps in your Kitchen Display: one for the "
"kitchen/bar and one for the service. You can configure steps in the kitchen "
"display configuration menu."
msgstr ""
"ປະຈຸບັນທ່ານມີສອງຂັ້ນຕອນໃນໜ້າຈໍສະແດງຜົນໃນເຮືອນຄົວ: ອັນໜຶ່ງສຳລັບເຮືອນຄົວ/ບາ ແລະ ອີກອັນໜຶ່ງສຳລັບການບໍລິກ"
"ານ. ທ່ານສາມາດຕັ້ງຄ່າຂັ້ນຕອນໄດ້ໃນເມນູການຕັ້ງຄ່າ Kitchen Display."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You didn't import demo data? You can still do it. Go to Apps  &amp;gt; "
"Industries  &amp;gt; Upgrade your Bar  &amp; Pub package and check the "
"related box"
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານບໍ່ໄດ້ນຳເຂົ້າຂໍ້ມູນສາທິດບໍ? ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດເຮັດໄດ້. ໄປທີ່ ແອັບ (Apps) &amp;gt; ກຸ່ມອຸດສາຫະກຳ "
"(Industries) &amp;gt; ອັບເກຣດຊຸດ Bar &amp; Pub ຂອງທ່ານ ແລະ ໝາຍເອົາຫ້ອງທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You have two main possibilities in Odoo to ease your replenishment process."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານມີສອງຄວາມເປັນໄປໄດ້ຫຼັກໃນ Odoo ເພື່ອຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ຂັ້ນຕອນການຕື່ມສິນຄ້າຂອງທ່ານງ່າຍຂຶ້ນ."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You just installed the Odoo for Bar package. By doing so, we have installed "
"a bunch of necessary apps to run your bar efficiently."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຫາກໍ່ຕິດຕັ້ງຊຸດ Odoo ສຳລັບບາ. ດ້ວຍການເຮັດແບບນີ້, ພວກເຮົາໄດ້ຕິດຕັ້ງແອັບທີ່ຈຳເປັນຈຳນວນໜຶ່ງເພື່ອໃຫ້ບາຂ"
"ອງທ່ານດຳເນີນງານໄດ້ຢ່າງມີປະສິດທິພາບ."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You should be able to execute the following flows to have an overview of "
"various flows you can quickly execute with this package using Odoo."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຄວນຈະສາມາດດຳເນີນການຕາມຂັ້ນຕອນຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ ເພື່ອໃຫ້ເຫັນພາບລວມຂອງຂັ້ນຕອນຕ່າງໆ ທີ່ທ່ານສາມາດເຮັດໄດ້ຢ່າ"
"ງວ່ອງໄວດ້ວຍຊຸດເຄື່ອງມືນີ້ໂດຍໃຊ້ Odoo."

